KG name: FOODpedia - Linked Data Dataset about Food Products and Ingredients
Description: At this moment FOODpedia contains information about only Russian food products and ingredients that was crawled from [GoodsMatrix](http://goodsmatrix.ru/) web site. Also it has links to ingredients from [AGROVOC](http://datahub.io/dataset/agrovoc-skos).
